───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────




            "Listen, Read, Look - Master!"
               v 2.5 (second edition)



Annotation

  This program is the computer course to those who begins
learning Russian language. It consists of floppy disk (5
lessons), audio cassettes and user's manual.
  This program may be used from floppy disk or hard disk.
It supports: EGA graphics in 640x350 resolution 16 colors;
Mouse; Russian keyboard (arrangement of the Russian letters
may be easy changed); restart system; system of help.


